text: Hans Mariacher (11 August 1910 - 24 June 1985) was an Austrian ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1910 births Category:1985 deaths Category:Austrian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Austria Category:Ski jumpers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:People from Kitzbühel
